                              SelectedIndex="0" Height="45" Width="250" 
                              VerticalAlignment="Center" HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                              FontFamily="Yu Gothic UI" FontSize="23" SelectionChanged="cmbClientsStatisticsType_SelectionChanged"
                                  DropDownClosed="cmbClientsStatisticsType_DropDownClosed">
                            <ComboBoxItem IsEnabled="False" Visibility="Collapsed" >
                                <TextBlock Background="Transparent" Foreground="LightGray">Статистика клиентов</TextBlock>
                            </ComboBoxItem>

                            <ComboBoxItem x:Name="cbiAge">
                                <TextBlock Background="Transparent" Foreground="Black">По возрасту</TextBlock>
                            </ComboBoxItem>

                            <ComboBoxItem x:Name="cbiGender">
                                <TextBlock Background="Transparent" Foreground="Black">По полу</TextBlock>
                            </ComboBoxItem>

                            <ComboBoxItem x:Name="cbiWorkField">
                                <TextBlock Background="Transparent" Foreground="Black">По деятельности</TextBlock>
                            </ComboBoxItem>
                        </ComboBox>
                    </Border>

                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Border>

        <Grid x:Name="mainGrid" Width="1230" ScrollViewer.VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled"
              Grid.Column="1" Background="Transparent" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Margin="0,0,0,0">
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="100" />
                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>

            <Border x:Name="borderCancelButton" Grid.Row="0" Height="40" Width="130" IsEnabled="True"
                        BorderBrush="#FFD9D9D9" BorderThickness="2" CornerRadius="5"
                        HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Center" Margin="10,0,0,0" 
                        Style="{StaticResource borderStyle}">
                <Button x:Name="btnCancel" Height="40" Width="130"  Style="{StaticResource buttonStyle}" TabIndex="10"
                            FontFamily="Yu Gothic UI" FontSize="30" Cursor="Hand"
                            HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" 
                            Content="Назад" Background="Transparent" Click="btnCancel_Click">

                </Button>
            </Border>

            <TextBlock Grid.Row="0" Foreground="Black" Text="Статистика" FontWeight="Medium"
                       Grid.ColumnSpan="3"
                       FontFamily="Yu Gothic UI Semilight" FontSize="36"
                       HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>

            <TextBlock x:Name="tbNothingFound" Visibility="Hidden" Grid.Row="1" FontFamily="Yu Gothic UI" 
                       FontSize="30" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Top"  Margin="0,100,0,0"
                       Foreground="#FF5D5D5D">Ничего не нашлось :(</TextBlock>

            <Border x:Name="statisticsBorder" Grid.Row="1" Margin="10" CornerRadius="10">
                <Border.Background>
                    <SolidColorBrush Color="White" Opacity="0.8"/>
                </Border.Background>

                <ScrollViewer HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Visible" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled">
                    <Grid>
                        <TextBlock Grid.Row="0" Foreground="Black" Text="Количество поездок" FontWeight="Medium"
                       Grid.ColumnSpan="3" x:Name="tbLineChartTitle" Visibility="Hidden"
                       FontFamily="Yu Gothic UI Semilight" FontSize="30"
                       HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                            <TextBlock.LayoutTransform>
                                <RotateTransform Angle="270" />
                            </TextBlock.LayoutTransform>
                        </TextBlock>
                        <Grid x:Name="gridForChart" Margin="5" Height="500" Width="1100">

                        </Grid>
                    </Grid>
                </ScrollViewer>

            </Border>

        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</UserControl>

